t: "Are you ňĻO Prophetňļ not aware of the one who argued with Abraham about his Lord because God had granted him kingship? ňĻRememberňļ when Abraham said, ‚ÄúMy Lord is the One Who has power to give life and cause death.‚ÄĚ He argued, ‚ÄúI too have the power to give life and cause death.‚ÄĚ Abraham challenged ňĻhimňļ, ‚ÄúGod causes the sun to rise from the east. So make it rise from the west.‚ÄĚ And so the disbeliever was dumbstruck. And God does not guide the wrongdoing people"